data.description: Highly sought after one story home in Rivers Edge all brick w/stone and NO CARPET. This is the perfect home for anyone. This home has a study/formal sitting and dining room that is perfect for holiday gatherings. Spacious kitchen with breakfast area that opens up to the living area. Primary bedroom located at rear with large closet and ensuite with separate tub and shower. Second and third rooms are very spacious with nearby gameroom/flex room and secondary bathroom. Sizeable backyard with covered patio that's perfect for cookouts.
